   <text type="translation">
      <body>
         <pb facs="1866_01_22_Kniffler_Nagasaki_von_Telge_Noelting_Shanghai_1.tif" n="1"/>
         <p>TELGE NÖLTING &amp; CO.<lb/>SHANGHAI.<lb/>per “Chusan” Shanghai 22nd January
                1866<lb/> Messrs. L. Kniffler+ Co<lb/>Nagasaki<lb/>We last had this pleasure on
                <lb/>the 10th of this month and have since received your esteemed <lb/>letter of the
                same date. Your remarks regarding the lead we <lb/>noted carefully and today have
                the pleasure of informing <lb/>you that we have sold the 1200 piculs IB at Tls
                5.0.95. with<lb/>a delivery time of four weeks. For the remaining amount<lb/>we were
                offered Tls 4.8. but we are still hoping to achieve <lb/>Tls 4.9. <lb/>Messrs.
                Arnemann + Co. Hong Kong drew <lb/>on us the amount of the invoice for the 200 pics.
                of saltpetre,<lb/>loaded for you on the “Child of the O⟨.”⟩, for $ 1702.12. at ⟨a⟩
                rate<lb/>of 74½% with Shanghai Tls 1268.08. We accepted this bill of
                exchange<lb/>for your esteemed invoice per 3rd February.<lb/>We noted your esteemed
                notifications with regard to the <lb/>weapons and our Mr. Nölting will likely be
                able to bring <lb/>this matter to a satisfying result during his presence<lb/>at
                your location. <lb/>The amount for the missing two pigs of lead <lb/>we will, in
                line with your wishes, deduct from the<lb/>net salvages of your share.
                <lb/>Regarding our market we can only confirm what<lb/>we said in our last letter.
                <lb/>Always awaiting your esteemed notifications with <lb/>great pleasure, we send
                our greetings, <lb/>Yours sincerely and respectfully <lb/>Telge Nölting + Co.<lb/>
                (Unfortunately the positive response from Nanking regarding the 2350 town
                markets<lb/> has still not arrived, but is expected to certainly have in a few<lb/>
                days<lb/> TNCo [?])</p>
         <pb facs="1866_01_22_Kniffler_Nagasaki_von_Telge_Noelting_Shanghai_2.tif" n="2"/>
         <pb facs="1866_01_22_Kniffler_Nagasaki_von_Telge_Noelting_Shanghai_3.tif" n="3"/>
         <pb facs="1866_01_22_Kniffler_Nagasaki_von_Telge_Noelting_Shanghai_4.tif" n="4"/>
         <p>⟨1866<lb/>Telge Nölting +Co.<lb/>Shanghai Jan. 22nd<lb/>R[eceived] Jan. 27th<lb/>2nd
